import{_ as t,c as o,b as a,o as p}from"./chunks/framework.Bh4f_7Kc.js";const f=JSON.parse('{"title":"","description":"","frontmatter":{},"headers":[],"relativePath":"guide/Longfellow.md","filePath":"guide/Longfellow.md"}'),s={name:"guide/Longfellow.md"};function n(r,e,i,l,h,d){return p(),o("div",null,e[0]||(e[0]=[a("<p>Do not lament to me with your melancholy rhymes, that life is but an empty dream! When the soul sleeps it is dead, and the body is no longer what it once was.</p><p>Life is real, it is not nothing; the grave is not its final place. &quot;For you are dust, and to dust you return&quot; - that does not refer to the soul.</p><p>Don&#39;t just indulge in pleasure and don&#39;t just complain; the path of life should have other goals - go and work hard, so that every tomorrow we will see that we are standing higher than we are today.</p><p>Art needs to last, but light is only fleeting. Although our hearts are brave and resolute, they still sound like the muffled drums of funerals, sending us to the grave.</p><p>The world is a vast battlefield, and life should be ready to fight at any time. Be a hero and fight bravely, don&#39;t be like a dumb animal driven by others.</p><p>Don&#39;t count on the future, no matter how happy it is, let the past years go to hell, God is above you, and your heart is in your heart, so do it, grab the lively present, do it.</p><p>---002---</p><p>When your hopes are dashed one by one, you must remain firm and calm!</p><p>---003---</p><p>There are three kinds of silence: one is not speaking; two is no desire; three is no thought.</p><p>---004---</p><p>In every life, some rain is bound to fall, and some days are destined to be dark and bleak.</p><p>---005---</p><p>Your life is like everyone else&#39;s, it rains in every life.</p><p>---006---</p><p>Don&#39;t always sigh for the past, it will never come back; improve the present wisely. Face the complicated and uncertain future with a resolute will without worry or fear.</p><p>---007---</p><p>How beautiful youth is! Glowing and full of color and fantasy, youth is the first chapter of a book, a story that never ends.</p><p>---008---</p><p>The path and destination of life is neither pleasure nor sorrow. Work hard for every tomorrow, every tomorrow is better than today.</p><p>---009---</p><p>Many people have talent, but if they don&#39;t use it, their talent will be buried.</p><p>---010---</p><p>The lines of a Lapland song are still remembered today: &quot;A child&#39;s wishes are the wishes of the wind, and youth&#39;s thoughts are long thoughts.&quot;</p><p>---011---</p><p>Geniuses have many quirks</p><p>---012---</p><p>Tell me not, in mornful numbers,</p><p>&quot;Life is but an empty dream!&quot;</p><p>For the soul is dead that slumber Tell me not, in mornful numbers,</p><p>&quot;Life is but an empty dream!&quot;</p><p>For the soul is dead that slumbers,</p><p>Things are not what they seem.</p><p>---013---</p><p>Self-improvement is the mother of luck</p><p>---014---</p><p>When I compare</p><p>Lost and gained,</p><p>Regrets and gains,</p><p>I just feel that there is very little meaning.</p><p>We know</p><p>How much time has been wasted;</p><p>Aspirations are like arrows shot from a bow.</p><p>Either the original intention was not achieved or it failed completely.</p><p>But who dares</p><p>Is this how you measure gains and losses?</p><p>Failure may be victory in disguise;</p><p>When the tide recedes, another huge wave comes.</p><p>---015---</p><p>Behind the dark clouds, the sun still blasts out flames</p><p>---016---</p><p>Only by trying can we achieve something</p><p>---017---</p><p>Keeping actions in mind, not creeds, will help meet our greatest needs</p><p>---018---</p><p>Failure may be success in disguise, and the lowest point is the beginning of the climax.</p><p>---019---</p><p>On the road of life, when your hopes are dashed one by one, you must remain firm and calm.</p><p>---020---</p><p>You only live once.</p><p>---021---</p><p>In personality, manners, demeanor and everything else, it is best to be simple</p><p>---022---</p><p>Youth is so beautiful! It is radiant, full of color and fantasy. It is the first chapter of a book and a story that never ends.</p><p>---023---</p><p>The painting that is closest to sculpture is the most perfect</p><p>---024---</p><p>The secret in my heart is the anniversary.</p><p>---025---</p><p>The pretty words on most people&#39;s lips are like roses that soldiers stick on the muzzles of their guns on holidays.</p><p>---026---</p><p>A prudent person always does things step by step.</p><p>---027---</p><p>My ambition is my only friend</p><p>---028---</p><p>Don&#39;t go to bed until you can say to yourself that you have learned something today. Sometimes we learn more from other people&#39;s mistakes than from their strengths.</p><p>---029---</p><p>Whether success or failure, it all depends on yourself.</p><p>---030---</p><p>Our destined goal and path is not pleasure or suffering, but action, to go one step further each tomorrow than we do today.</p><p>---031---</p><p>The pen can cause the deepest wounds to people.</p><p>---032---</p><p>Only labor can bring people happiness.</p><p>---033---</p><p>Sunday - the golden day that brings together the time scrolls of a week.</p><p>---034---</p><p>I shot an arrow into the sky, but I didn&#39;t know where it landed.</p><p>---035---</p><p>Walking without a guide, you often get lost</p><p>---036---</p><p>We sometimes learn more from our mistakes than from our virtues.</p><p>---037---</p><p>Life is honest, life is sincere, and the grave is not its end.</p><p>---038---</p><p>Leaves are to the forest as children are to the world.</p><p>---039---</p><p>If you want to hit a swan, you have to aim slightly higher than the swan, because the arrow will be affected by the earth&#39;s gravity when it leaves the string.</p><p>---040---</p><p>Under the blow of fate, I bled but never bowed my head.</p><p>---041---</p><p>When it rains, people can only let it rain.</p><p>---042---</p><p>Some people are like folk songs, popular only for a short time.</p><p>---043---</p><p>A person only has one youth in his life.</p><p>---044---</p><p>Youth is full of color and fantasy. It is the first chapter of a book and a story that never ends.</p><p>---045---</p><p>Don&#39;t go to bed until you can say to yourself that you have learned something today. Sometimes we learn more from other people&#39;s mistakes than from their strengths.</p><p>---046---</p><p>Keep harvesting, keep pursuing, you will always learn to work hard and wait</p><p>---047---</p><p>How beautiful youth is! Glowing and full of color and fantasy, it is the first chapter of a book and a story that never ends.</p><p>---048---</p><p>Let us get up and work, and have the courage to take on any fate: keep making progress, keep pursuing, be good at working, and be good at waiting.</p><p>---049---</p><p>Don&#39;t tell me with sad words that life is just a false dream.</p>",118)]))}const m=t(s,[["render",n]]);export{f as __pageData,m as default};
